      <h2>Corporate Profile</h2>
      <div id="left-content" align="left">
        <h4>Multi-Fold Links Inc. </h4>
        <div id="headlinesContent">
          <p class="ContentFontA">Established in 1987, MFL, Inc. has acquired cumulative experience in the field of information and communications technology, electronics, electrical engineering, mechanical engineering, interior architecture and systems integration.</p>
        </div>
        <h4>Our Mission</h4>
        <div id="headlinesContent">
        <p><b>We are in the people business providing the right information and communications technology solutions. </b></p>
        </div>
        <h4>Our Vision</h4>
        <div id="headlinesContent">
          <p class="ContentFontA"><b>We aim to be the vendor-of-choice to those who seek ICT-centric business and process solutions in the local and foreign markets.</b> </p>        
        </div>
        <h4>Multi-Fold Links Inc. Directors</h4>
        <div id="headlinesContent">
          <p class="ContentFontA"><strong>Mr. Edgardo B. Favila, President and CEO of Multi-Fold Links, Inc.,</strong> An ICT practitioner for more than 30 years, received education from San Beda College and the University of the Philippines.<br><br></p>
          <p class="ContentFontA"><strong>Mr. Jovencio C. Kintanar, Director of Multi-Fold Links, Inc.,</strong> An ICT practitioner for more than 30 years and former President Adviser for Information and Communication Technology, received education from Ateneo de Manila and the University of the Philippines.<br><br></p>
          <p class="ContentFontA"><strong>Mr. Augusto M. Cosio, Jr., Director of Multi-Fold Links, Inc.,</strong> a Corporate Finance and Investment Banking practitioner for more than 30 years, received education from Ateneo de Manila and the University of the Philippines.<br><br></p>
          <p class="ContentFontA"><strong>Atty. Cesar Evangelista, Director of Multi-Fold Links, Inc.,</strong> Director of Multi-Fold Links, Inc., a legal practitioner for more than 25 years, received education from the San Beda College of Law and an MA from the University of Santo Tomas College of Law.<br><br></p>
          <p class="ContentFontA"><strong>Col. Teodoro Runes(PMA 1971), Director of Multi-Fold Links,</strong> Inc., a security management practitioner for more than 30 years, received education from the Philippine Military Academy.<br><br></p>
          <p class="ContentFontA"><strong>Ms. Arlyn L. Solitario, Director of Multi-Fold Links, Inc. and Chief Operating Officer,</strong>   an office administration and marketing practitioner for more than 20 years, received education from the Polytechnic University of the Philippines.<br><br></p>
          <p class="ContentFontA"><strong>Mr. Karl R. Favila, Director of Multi-Fold Links, Inc. and Chief Channels Officer,</strong> an international business development and ICT practitioner for more than 4 years, received education from Reedley International School and the University of Asia and the Pacific.<br><br></p>
        </div>                      
